  - Fix them or document blockers/root causes.
  - Ensure CI prevents merging new critical/high vulns.
- [ ] **2. Code‑Scanning & Dependabot Backlog:**
  - Baseline: 5,000+ code scanning alerts, 253 Dependabot vulnerabilities.
